    <item>
      <title>MacWispr 1.2.5</title>
      <link>https://github.com/vasanthsreeram/macwispr/releases/tag/v1.2.5</link>
      <sparkle:version>1.2.5</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 03:16:42 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>MacWispr 1.2.5</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Much smaller update</strong> — polish model no longer inside the app (~1.2 GB → ~44 MB zip)</li>
          <li><strong>Polish download-on-enable</strong> — optional Local LLM polish downloads ~400 MB (4-bit) from Hugging Face only if you turn it on</li>
          <li><strong>Leaner packaging</strong> — single Metal shader library (no duplicate metallibs)</li>
          <li>ASR models still download separately as before</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
