    <item>
      <title>MacWispr 1.2.4</title>
      <link>https://github.com/vasanthsreeram/macwispr/releases/tag/v1.2.4</link>
      <sparkle:version>1.2.4</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 18:38:22 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>MacWispr 1.2.4</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Live Qwen partials</strong> — draft transcript while you hold ⌥Space; card grows with text</li>
          <li><strong>Faster release paste</strong> — reuses live draft when already complete (no multi-second re-STT)</li>
          <li><strong>Polish off by default</strong> — raw STT insert; enable Local/OpenAI polish in Settings</li>
          <li><strong>Mic input picker</strong> — choose built-in / AirPods / USB</li>
          <li><strong>Window + history fixes</strong> — single dashboard, Cmd+Q, cleaner history</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
