      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>MacWispr 1.2.3</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Parakeet v3</strong> — on-device En + EU (Core ML / Neural Engine)</li>
          <li><strong>Qwen 0.6B / 1.7B</strong> — En + Asian (MLX), RAM-aware defaults</li>
          <li><strong>Model quick-switch</strong> — dashboard Local chip</li>
          <li><strong>GPU free on model switch</strong> — MLX unload + Metal cache clear</li>
          <li><strong>Parakeet short-clip fix</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Developer ID + notarized</strong> — Accessibility survives updates</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Ships from <code>main</code> only. Fine-tuned LFM polish is not included (separate branch).</p>
      ]]></description>
